contents.text: We can write text within markers to modify the presentation. The following text appears within a 'Highlight' marker and will be highlighted in the formatted test report.
The following text contains a 'Link' marker to create a link to a Url.

entry.value: <summary> This demo shows how different parts of the log can be isolated into separate log streams. Gallio sends some output to built-in log streams automatically. You can write to these built-in log streams or create log streams of your own. </summary>

contents.text: Console error messages go into the 'ConsoleError' stream.
Console output messages go into the 'ConsoleOutput' stream.
Debug... ... and Trace messages go into the 'DebugTrace' stream.
Log messages go into the 'Log' stream.
Log messages can also go into a custom stream of your choice.
